# 懵然不知
(pos:成語)
<explanation>
yue:指人對某件事完全唔知、完全唔明白，好似頭昏腦脹咁，對情況毫無所知（量詞：個）
eng:to be completely unaware; to be totally in the dark
<eg>
yue:呢個新聞好突然，我哋完全懵然不知。 (nei1 go1 xin1un2 hou2 dou1 dan1, ngo5 dei6 wai4m4 fan1 san1 mong1 jan4 bu1 zi2.)
eng:This news was so sudden; we were completely unaware of it. [end of text]


